title: Fix window focus in image/document/chart viewers
commitTitle: Fix window focus in image/document/chart viewers [741b1a4]
commitBody: Added .focus() calls after window.open() in three viewer iframes: image-viewer.html (single image viewer popup), document-viewer.html (document viewer popup), and single-chart-viewer.html (chart popup). Ensures all popup windows are brought to foreground when opened from PWA in Chrome.

title: Fix window focus in request-form for all popup windows
commitTitle: Fix window focus in request-form for all popup windows [4a31c82]
commitBody: Added .focus() calls after window.open() in request-form-core.js for 4 windows: charity trustees, officer appointments, osprey-tab (matter history), and ID image viewer. Ensures all popup windows are brought to foreground when opened from PWA in Chrome.

title: Fix osprey-tab focus in uk-sanctions-checker
commitTitle: Fix osprey-tab focus in uk-sanctions-checker [a1449f7]
commitBody: Added .focus() call after window.open() in uk-sanctions-checker.html to ensure the osprey-tab is brought to foreground when opening matter history links from PWA. Completes the fix started in client-details.html.

title: Fix osprey-tab not focusing when opened from PWA
commitTitle: Fix osprey-tab not focusing when opened from PWA [3b42f58]
commitBody: Added .focus() calls after window.open() to ensure the osprey-tab is brought to foreground when opening matter history links from PWA installed via Chrome. Previously the tab would open but remain hidden in the background.

title: Fix retry button styling to match abort button
commitTitle: Fix retry button styling to match abort button [decdd95]
commitBody: Changed retry button from filled orange to outlined style with bold orange text and orange border. Matches abort button design pattern exactly.

title: Retry card styling refinements - match abort/monitoring card design
commitTitle: Retry card styling refinements - match abort/monitoring card design [b15353c]
commitBody: Removed solid left border, removed warning icon, moved button to top right, updated to use Transport/RotisRegular fonts, changed all text to grey #666, made labels bold grey. Card now matches sleek design of abort and monitoring cards.

title: IDV document retry system - track upload failures and enable retries
commitTitle: IDV document retry system - track upload failures and enable retries [2680378]
commitBody: Replaces abort logic with retry mechanism. Tracks failed uploads in uploadAttempts array. Shows ERROR badge and retry card in checks manager. Smart retry: reuses same images for network errors, finds alternatives for 422 rejections. Reverted patch-abort to v2 transactions only.

title: Fix PDF filename to use friendly name with request type and client name
commitTitle: Fix PDF filename to use friendly name with request type and client name [d3379e7]
commitBody: Updated getClientNameForFilename to check cD.n (full name) first. Updated filename generation to also check messageData for client name. Added logging to debug filename generation. This fixes filename to show 'Form J Request - Client Name' instead of 'request 1 - client'.

title: Fix PDF margins and ensure Trebuchet MS font is used
commitTitle: Fix PDF margins and ensure Trebuchet MS font is used [4781a62]
commitBody: Updated request form PDF generation to use proper 10mm margins and ensure Trebuchet MS font is used instead of custom base64 fonts. Body padding set to 10mm and PDF image positioned with 10mm margins.

title: Fix html2canvas and jsPDF loading for request form PDF generation
commitTitle: Fix html2canvas and jsPDF loading for request form PDF generation [bf6c9a3]
commitBody: Added separate script tags for html2canvas and jsPDF libraries. Updated code to handle jsPDF from UMD bundle namespace. This fixes the 'library not loaded' error.

title: Fix request form PDF generation using printJS approach (html2canvas + jsPDF)
commitTitle: Fix request form PDF generation using printJS approach (html2canvas + jsPDF) [23eb0f5]
commitBody: Updated generateRequestPDF to use html2canvas + jsPDF directly (same approach printJS uses internally) instead of html2pdf wrapper. This should fix blank PDF issue by properly rendering HTML with styles applied.

title: Replace print dialog with direct PDF download and osprey-tab integration
commitTitle: Replace print dialog with direct PDF download and osprey-tab integration [d193f6a]
commitBody: Updated uk-sanctions-checker.html and request-form-core.js to download PDFs directly instead of opening print dialog. PDFs download with friendly filenames and osprey-tab opens immediately after download. Downloads occur even when no link is provided.

title: Add REFERENCE field to electronic-id check header
commitTitle: Add REFERENCE field to electronic-id check header [b3bd9fa]
commitBody: Added REFERENCE field to detail header card for electronic-id checks only. Displays the reference sent to clients in SMS (from thirdfortResponse.ref). Field appears in header meta grid alongside Transaction ID and dates. Not shown for lite-screen, IDV, or KYB checks.

title: Remove mock data and functions, fix task card display for aborted checks
commitTitle: Remove mock data and functions, fix task card display for aborted checks [12ab43b]
commitBody: Removed loadMockChecks function and mock data. Removed 'Load Mock Checks' button from HTML. Fixed task card display to hide 'Task in progress' text for aborted checks while retaining it for open/processing checks. Added 'pending' status to open check detection. Improved task/report detection for KYB checks.

title: Fix address task breakdown, add mock checks, and improve task card summaries
commitTitle: Fix address task breakdown, add mock checks, and improve task card summaries [a66713b]
commitBody: Fixed address task breakdown handling for lite-screen/IDV checks to properly map footprint data. Added recalculation logic for address task results. Added 'Load Mock Checks' button on loading screen with 3 sample checks. Fixed aborted checks to show requested tasks. Added collapsed summaries for screening (0 matches found) and address (X sources verified) tasks. Fixed ongoing monitoring display for aborted checks.

title: Add missing renderTaskAnnotations function
commitTitle: Add missing renderTaskAnnotations function [213b77a]
commitBody: Added renderTaskAnnotations function to fix TypeError when rendering task cards for closed checks. Function filters and groups annotations by task type and renders them using existing CSS classes.

title: Fix task cards not populating for closed checks
commitTitle: Fix task cards not populating for closed checks [c6d53c3]
commitBody: Changed condition in createTaskCard to check check.status instead of outcome.status, ensuring task details are displayed for all closed checks regardless of individual task outcome status.

title: Standardize address autocomplete and country normalization across all iframes
commitTitle: Standardize address autocomplete and country normalization across all iframes [d4aa9c6]
commitBody: Added comprehensive normalizeCountryCode() function to jurisdiction-autocomplete.js with full ISO country code support. Updated all iframes (thirdfort-check, request-form, client-details, image-uploader) to normalize country codes when loading, saving, and formatting addresses. Fixed infinite loop in request-form validation by adding guards and debouncing. Removed excessive console logging.

title: Remove mock data and comment out sensitive console.log statements
commitTitle: Remove mock data and comment out sensitive console.log statements [e70d7ad]
commitBody: Removed all mock data definitions, buttons, and event listeners. Commented out console.log statements that log client data to prevent sensitive information exposure in production.

title: Update audit-log to show all status badges and FE Update markers together
commitTitle: Update audit-log to show all status badges and FE Update markers together [7917796]

commitTitle: Update audit-log PDF to use print.js with print-friendly styling [da3086a]

title: Fix birthdate display and add comprehensive country flags
commitTitle: Fix birthdate display and add comprehensive country flags [5ee6026]
commitBody: Fixed [object Object] display issue for birthdate in PEP cards by adding extractDob helper function. Added comprehensive country flag mappings including Canada and 100+ other countries with case-insensitive matching.

title: Add current-check message handler for refresh-entry response
commitTitle: Add current-check message handler for refresh-entry response [eca233e]
commitBody: Added current-check postMessage handler that responds with refresh-entry message containing the currently open check ID (or undefined if in list view).

title: Add transaction details to SOF PDF and open-check message handler
commitTitle: Add transaction details to SOF PDF and open-check message handler [58bf906]
commitBody: SOF PDF now shows individual transactions with links/comments/flags instead of just summary counts. Added open-check postMessage handler to allow parent to open specific checks by ID.

title: Fix emoji encoding with byte-level file I/O
commitTitle: Fix emoji encoding with byte-level file I/O [5baf66e]
commitBody: Replaced ReadAllText/WriteAllText with byte-level Read-Utf8File/Write-Utf8File functions to prevent PowerShell from re-encoding Unicode characters during regex operations. This preserves emojis and other Unicode characters in HTML files.
